{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_03_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 零れる弱音",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインデー前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2……ここで、こう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2… Here‚ like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr001-02.m4a",
      "text": "このステップにしたら……もっとかっこ良くなるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I do the steps like this… Wouldn’t it look a little cooler?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.479711024,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 14.479711024
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5100,
          "startTime": 14.579711024
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん。お疲れ様で～す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ hello {user}-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。バレンタインイベント出演のために\nこころがリズノワの新曲を企画してるそうじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job. I heard that Kokoro is planning\na new song by LizNoir for the Valentine's Day event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4130443573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ～\nアイデアが溢れ出過ぎて、困っちゃうくらいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right~\nI'm so full of ideas‚ it's getting difficult!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.879711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……自分の才能が恐ろしいです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… I'm scared of my own talent",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。楽しみにしているからな\n無理だけはするなよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I'll be looking forward to it\nDon't push yourself too hard‚ OK?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.879711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "は～い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "OK~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8130443573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワらしいバレンタインを全力でお見せしますよ～\n期待して待ってて下さいね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll show you a Liznoir-like Valentine’s Day with all my might~\nI hope you’re looking forward to it~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2463776906,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1300.0000000000043,
          "startTime": 52.5463776906
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4463776906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "どうも～。お疲れ様でーす……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello~ Thank you for your hard work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.379711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こころ？　お疲れ様\n今日は休みだよな、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro? Hello.\nToday was your day off. Something the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5130443573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、いえ、たまにはふらっとこんな風に\n事務所に来るのもいいかな～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ no‚ I think it would be nice\nto come to the office like this sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、「休みの日も会社に来るなんて感心だな！」\nって評価する古いタイプの人もいるじゃないですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think about it‚ “I’m proud of you for coming to work even on your days off!”\nThere are old people who might say that‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.379711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "古いタイプの人って言ってる時点でダメだろう……\n俺はそんな評価はしないよ。休める時に休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're wrong at the point of saying 'old people'…\nI don't make that assessment. Take a break when you're resting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.179711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "う……っ。それなら……アレです、アレ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Then… That's it‚ that's it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.879711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、{user}さんって\n気の抜けた顔をしてるじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ {user}-san‚ you always\nhave a listless face!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.479711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、{user}さんを見てると\nこころも気が抜けて落ち着くんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ when looking at {user}-san‚\nit makes Kokoro powerless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そこはせめて、癒やされるって言ってくれよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At least call that \"refreshing\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6130443573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "今のは冗談ですよ～。本当は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I said just is a joke~ Actually…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんやすずにゃんをどうからかっていくか\n方針を相談したいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to discuss\nhow to make fun of Ai-chan and Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "たっぷりタメておいてそれか……\n何か他に話したいことがあるんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what you're saying after a long conversation…\nIsn't there something else you want to say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.079711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "う……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.579711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、確かにあの子達のからかい方は\nいくらでも思いつくんですけど～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I can definitely think of ways\nto make fun of those two‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ほどほどにしてくれよ……？\nこころ。俺はこころのマネージャーだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's enough. Okay…?\nKokoro. I'm Kokoro's manager",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.379711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "悩みがあるなら、話せる範囲でいいから教えてくれ\nとりあえず喋るだけで楽になることもあると思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any concerns‚ please let me know as long as you can say.\nI think it might be easier just to talk about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.279711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "むぅ……{user}さん、やりおる\nやりおりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… {user}-san‚ pretty good huh?\nYou are pretty good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "人の弱った心につけいるのがお上手です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're good at digging in while people's minds got weak!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "言い方が悪過ぎるだろ……\nそれに、弱った心って自分で言ってるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel some malice in the words…\nBesides‚ you said yourself that your heart got weak.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.8463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
